[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     56[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     57[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Everything that is configuration rather than logic lives here. Resource names, model IDs, the seam-detection rule library, the transition-of-care protocol library, the referral-lifecycle state machine, and the consent-posture defaults are what you would change between environments.
