[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1731[0m:[38;5;10m[49m class FHIRMedicationRequestAdapter:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1732[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """Parses FHIR MedicationRequest resources."""
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1733[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
