[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2550[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Returns the composed response, the tool-call audit trail,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2551[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     and the citation set.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2552[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2553[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # Step 5A: assemble the system prompt with speaker-role-
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2554[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # aware behavior, citation discipline, and scope.
