[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3141[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The output-safety step does six things in order. First, scope filter (no diagnosis, no prescription). Second, persona-and-tone check (no companion-pattern, no clinician-impersonation). Third, faithfulness verification (every coordination-state assertion grounded in citation). Fourth, speaker-role disclosure check (honor caregiver carve-outs). Fifth, conservative-bias check (defer to care team where clinical judgment is involved). Sixth, persist the durable coordination-decision-record entry with full audit trail. A response that fails any check is replaced with a safe-template fallback rather than delivered.
