[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3147[0m:[38;5;10m[49m When a discharge event arrives, the assistant initiates the appropriate transition-of-care workflow. The workflow is a Step Functions state machine, version-controlled, signed off by clinical leadership, with deterministic state transitions and explicit completion criteria.
