[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3154[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Functions execution, persists the transition record,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3155[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     and emits the transition-initiated event.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3156[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3157[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # Step 7A: select the appropriate protocol.
