[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3175[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         input=json.dumps(workflow_input))
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3176[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3177[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # Step 7C: persist the transition record with the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3178[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # protocol-defined steps and their initial status.
