[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     }))
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # Step 7D: schedule the welcome-home check-in via
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # Pinpoint. Production has the Step Functions workflow
