[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     pinpoint_client.send_messages(
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         ApplicationId=PINPOINT_APPLICATION_ID,
